movies.title: The SpongeBob Movie: Sponge on the Run
movies.title_english: The SpongeBob Movie: Sponge on the Run
movies.title_long: The SpongeBob Movie: Sponge on the Run (2020)
movies.summary: Set before the events of the television series, SpongeBob goes on a trip to Kamp Koral and meets some new friends. However, when his pet snail Gary gets kidnapped by Poseidon and taken to the Lost City of Atlantic City, he and his new best friend Patrick must go on a rescue mission to save him from the dastardly plan of Poseidon before it is too late. The movie will also reveal the first time our beloved characters (as kids) met at Camp...a magical moment that brings meaning to the power of true friendship.

movies.title: Broken Swords: The Last in Line
movies.title_english: Broken Swords: The Last in Line
movies.title_long: Broken Swords: The Last in Line (2018)
movies.summary: Twelve seasoned men and women are on the run. If anyone can survive this, they will or they will die trying. And many will indeed die before the night bleeds away into morning light.

movies.title: Two Night Stand
movies.summary: After an extremely regrettable one night stand, two strangers wake up to find themselves snowed in after sleeping through a blizzard that put all of Manhattan on ice. They're now trapped together in a tiny apartment, forced to get to know each other way more than any one night stand should.

movies.title: Conspiracy
movies.summary: In January 1942, as the United States enters World War II, a conference assembles near Berlin. S.S. General Heydrich and his associate, Lieutenant Eichmann call the meeting to discuss the "evacuation" of Germany's Jews and other undesirables, a code word for their extermination in concentration camps. To begin this Final Solution, they must change the mind of a small group of men opposed to the idea, led by Chancellor Kritzinger.
